value.0: The droid’s body thrums quietly as it idles, though every so often it seems to turn and steal a furtive glance at the oversized mag-crane beside it. The impassive, expressionless metal exterior of the GNK-series seems to belie a star-crossed affection for the much larger piece of machinery. Or maybe you’re just overthinking things.
